@startuml Reports Activity

start

:Select Report Type;
note right
  Report Types:
  * Medicine Inventory
  * Family Planning
  * Deworming
  * BP Monitoring
  * Blood Sugar
  * Tetanus Toxoid
end note

if (Date Range Required?) then (yes)
  :Select Date Range;
  :Enter From Date;
  :Enter To Date;
endif

:Generate Report;

if (Generation Success?) then (yes)
  :Open PDF in New Tab;
else (no)
  :Show Error Message;
endif

stop

@enduml 